title: find my windows 11 product key - Microsoft Q&A
text: 1 The method depends on what type of Office licence you have, are you experiencing activation errors after the upgrade? 2 Click your Start Button, type cmd then right click Command Prompt and choose 'Run as Administrator' Run or paste this command and hit Enter: slmgr.vbs /dlv Please post a screenshot of the resulting dialog 3 Download the free ShowKeyPlus app from the Microsoft Store. Please provide a screenshot of that app window and please hide your product key in the screenshot.
